				<wikidot:authorName>Modern_Erasmus</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3129691</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I liked Joyce, but the dialogue of most of the characters she interacted with all seemed unnatural.</p> <p>The fact that only one small research team would be working on a global phenomenon like this also breaks my immersion hardcore, as does the decision on leadership being left to a site director and Joyce being able to unilaterally claim it when Young shot herself.</p> 
				 	]]>
